prompt: Compare the formatting menus at the top of these two word processors. Which of the following is a similarity between the two programs?
feedback: There are a lot of similarities between these two word processors, but there are also a lot of differences. They both have a way to get help... but they’re not both icons. One has a question mark icon, and the other has a menu item called “Help.” They don’t both have a “Review” menu area or a “Share” option... so those are differences between the two. They do both use similar icons for bold, italic, and underlined text, though... That’s one similarity they have in common.
